848
00:35:36,880 --> 00:35:37,880
To them who love God,

849
00:35:37,880 --> 00:35:39,559
to them who are the called according to his purpose.

850
00:35:39,559 --> 00:35:41,559
And we know this.

851
00:35:41,559 --> 00:35:44,239
So this evening, I don't know

852
