857
00:35:58,199 --> 00:36:00,079
Something that we face.

858
00:36:00,079 --> 00:36:04,199
And so how can we have faith through the trial?

859
00:36:04,199 --> 00:36:05,799
How can we have faith through the trial?

860
00:36:05,799 --> 00:36:07,160
I hope this evening,

861
00:36:07,160 --> 00:36:10,359
these are some super practical points, tips,

862
00:36:10,359 --> 00:36:11,759
that will help each and every one of us.

863
00:36:11,759 --> 00:36:13,799
And we'll remember Abraham.

864
00:36:13,799 --> 00:36:17,139
By faith, Abraham, when he was tried.

865
00:36:17,139 --> 00:36:17,979
And what did he do?

866
